PART 2 : DATASET DETAILS
Dataset Name
“Internal Mobile Payment Session Dataset” (no official external name).
The dataset consists of sensor and interaction recordings from a custom mobile application (PhonePe‑like).
The raw data is stored as JSON files (one per user), but the project works exclusively with pre‑extracted CSV features.
The CSV files are generated by SessionLevelFeatureExtractor and placed in a folder named features/ (or features/v2/ for newer runs).

Source / Link
Source: Company’s internal data collection – not publicly available.

Raw format: Each user has a single .json file containing multiple sessions (touches, sensor events, navigation).

Feature CSVs: Generated by running SessionPipeline.run() for each user. This writes two CSV files per user:

{user_id}_training_sessions.csv

{user_id}_testing_sessions.csv

